  m_Name: GSWD_Course_1_Final_Assessment_Q1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestionData
  question: 'A national weather service uses data analytics to analyze weather in
    one part of the country. The weather service uses the results to determine future
    weather conditions in other parts of the country.

    What type of analytics
    is the national weather service using?'
  answers:
  - Predictive analytics
  - Diagnostic analytics
  - Descriptive analytics
  - Prescriptive analytics
  maxSelections: 1
  correctAnswerIndices: 00000000
  correctMessage: In this scenario, the national weather service is using historical
    data to forecast weather conditions in other parts of the country.
  incorrectMessage: Not quite. Consider that the national weather service is forecasting
    based on historical data.
